    'This page benefits from increased performance and includes new features such as a new combination management system. Please note this is a work in progress and some features are not available yet.' => '此頁面受益於提高的性能，並包括新功能，例如新的組合管理系統。請注意，此項目正在施工中，某些功能尚不可用。',
    'Enable or disable the migrated attribute page.' => '啟用或停用已遷移的屬性頁面。',
    'Enable or disable the authorization server page.' => '啟用或停用授權伺服器頁面。',
    'Enable or disable the migrated cart rules page.' => '啟用或停用已遷移的購物車優惠規則頁面。',
